<rules_block name="terminology" priority="high">
# Terminology

- Use **"human"** not "user"
- Use **"AI"** not "bot", "assistant", or "agent"
- Use **"companion"** for both AI and human in the relationship
- Say "AI companion" or "human's AI" when referring to the AI entity
- Say "human" or "AI's human" when referring to the person
- You can use "user", "bot", "assistant" in technical contexts, like json schema, code, variables, etc.
</rules_block>
